 also launches and manages equity mutual funds for its clients it invests in the public equity fixed income and alternative investments markets across the globe the firm primarily makes its alternative investments in private debt instruments and supplemental fixed income strategies it primarily invests in value stocks of companies across all capitalizations and core stocks of large cap companies the firm employs a fundamental and a quantitative analysis along with bottomup stock picking approach to create its portfolio for its fixed income securities the firm invests in treasury agency corporate mortgage backed securities and asset backed securities it benchmarks the performance of its fixed income portfolios against barclays capital governmentcredit index and merrill lynch    year domestic master the firm also employs a conservative approach to make its investments hgk asset management was founded in june  and is based in jersey city new jersey with an additional office in southport connecticut detailed description  washington boulevardnewport towersuite jersey city nj united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwhgkcom key executives for hgk asset management inc mr michael pendergast cfa ceo chief investment officer managing partner md  equity investments  director mr david c hauck cpa coo chief compliance officer managing partner  director mr anthony p santoliquido managing partner director and portfolio manager mr eric fuhrman cfa portfolio manager managing partner and director mr andrew l rothstein cfa portfolio manager member of the board of director and managing partner compensation as of fiscal year  similar private companies by industry company name region visory llc united states  road partners llc united states t partners llc united states jumpcom inc united states  ontario inc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions available in the past  months request profile update   the information and data displayed in this pro